{"id":846,"parent_id":828,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":846,"title":"Ezekiel 18","subtitle":"","short_title":"Ezek.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 18"],[".studySummary",["i","Men will be punished for their own sins—Sinners will die, and the righteous will surely live—A righteous man who sins will be damned, and a sinner who repents will be saved."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.1","order":"02.27.018.56134"},["b","1"],"The word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"came unto me again, saying,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.2","order":"02.27.018.56135"},["b","2"],"What mean ye, that ye use this proverb concerning the land of Israel, saying, The fathers have eaten sour",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"grapes"],", and the children’s teeth are set on edge?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.3","order":"02.27.018.56136"},["b","3"],["i","As"],"I live, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],", ye shall not have",["i","occasion"],"any more to use this proverb in Israel."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.4","order":"02.27.018.56137"},["b","4"],"Behold, all souls are mine; as the soul of the father, so also the soul of the son is mine: the soul that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"sinneth"],", it shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"die"],"."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.5","order":"02.27.018.56138"},["b","5"],"¶But if a man be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"just"],", and do that which is lawful and right,"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.6","order":"02.27.018.56139"},["b","6"],["i","And"],"hath not eaten upon the mountains, neither hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"lifted up"],"his eyes to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"idols"],"of the house of Israel, neither hath",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"defiled"],"his neighbour’s wife, neither hath come near to a menstruous",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_6d"},"woman"],","],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.7","order":"02.27.018.56140"},["b","7"],"And hath not oppressed any,",["i","but"],"hath restored to the debtor his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"pledge"],", hath spoiled none by violence, hath given his bread to the hungry, and hath covered the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"naked"],"with a garment;"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.8","order":"02.27.018.56141"},["b","8"],"He",["i","that"],"hath not given forth upon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"usury"],", neither hath taken any increase,",["i","that"],"hath withdrawn his hand from iniquity, hath executed true judgment between man and man,"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.9","order":"02.27.018.56142"},["b","9"],"Hath walked in my statutes, and hath kept my judgments, to deal truly; he",["i","is"],"just, he shall surely live, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.10","order":"02.27.018.56143"},["b","10"],"¶If he beget a son",["i","that is"],"a robber, a shedder of blood, and",["i","that"],"doeth the like to",["i","any"],"one of these",["i","things,"]],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.11","order":"02.27.018.56144"},["b","11"],"And that doeth not any of those",["i","duties,"],"but even hath eaten upon the mountains, and defiled his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"neighbour’s"],"wife,"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.12","order":"02.27.018.56145"},["b","12"],"Hath oppressed the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"poor"],"and needy, hath spoiled by violence, hath not restored the pledge, and hath lifted up his eyes to the idols, hath committed abomination,"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.13","order":"02.27.018.56146"},["b","13"],"Hath given forth upon usury, and hath taken increase: shall he then live? he shall not live: he hath done all these abominations; he shall surely die; his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"blood"],"shall be upon him."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.14","order":"02.27.018.56147"},["b","14"],"¶Now, lo,",["i","if"],"he beget a son, that seeth all his father’s sins which he hath done, and considereth, and doeth not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"such like"],","],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.15","order":"02.27.018.56148"},["b","15"],["i","That"],"hath not eaten upon the mountains, neither hath lifted up his eyes to the idols of the house of Israel, hath not defiled his neighbour’s wife,"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.16","order":"02.27.018.56149"},["b","16"],"Neither hath oppressed any, hath not withholden the pledge, neither hath spoiled by violence,",["i","but"],"hath given his bread to the hungry, and hath covered the naked with a garment,"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.17","order":"02.27.018.56150"},["b","17"],["i","That"],"hath taken off his hand from the poor,",["i","that"],"hath not received usury nor increase, hath executed my judgments, hath walked in my statutes; he shall not die for the iniquity of his father, he shall surely live."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.18","order":"02.27.018.56151"},["b","18"],["i","As for"],"his father, because he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"cruelly"],"oppressed, spoiled his brother by violence, and did",["i","that"],"which",["i","is"],"not good among his people, lo, even he shall die in his iniquity."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.19","order":"02.27.018.56152"},["b","19"],"¶Yet say ye, Why? doth not the son bear the iniquity of the father? When the son hath done that which is lawful and right,",["i","and"],"hath kept all my statutes, and hath done them, he shall surely live."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.20","order":"02.27.018.56153"},["b","20"],"The soul that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"sinneth"],", it shall die. The son shall not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"bear"],"the iniquity of the father, neither shall the father bear the iniquity of the son: the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"righteousness"],"of the righteous shall be upon him, and the wickedness of the wicked shall be upon him."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.21","order":"02.27.018.56154"},["b","21"],"But if the wicked will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"turn"],"from all his sins that he hath committed, and keep all my statutes, and do that which is lawful and right, he shall surely live, he shall not die."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.22","order":"02.27.018.56155"},["b","22"],"All his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"transgressions"],"that he hath committed, they shall not be mentioned unto him: in his righteousness that he hath done he shall live."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.23","order":"02.27.018.56156"},["b","23"],"Have I any",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"pleasure"],"at all that the wicked should die? saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],":",["i","and"],"not that he should return from his ways, and live?"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.24","order":"02.27.018.56157"},["b","24"],"¶But when the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"righteous"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"turneth"],"away from his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_24c"},"righteousness"],", and committeth iniquity,",["i","and"],"doeth according to all the abominations that the wicked",["i","man"],"doeth, shall he live? All his righteousness that he hath done shall not be mentioned: in his trespass that he hath trespassed, and in his",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_24d"},"sin"],"that he hath sinned, in them shall he die."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.25","order":"02.27.018.56158"},["b","25"],"¶Yet ye say, The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"way"],"of the Lord is not",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"equal"],". Hear now, O house of Israel; Is not my way equal? are not your ways unequal?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.26","order":"02.27.018.56159"},["b","26"],"When a righteous",["i","man"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"turneth"],"away from his righteousness, and committeth iniquity, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"dieth"],"in them; for his iniquity that he hath done shall he die."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.27","order":"02.27.018.56160"},["b","27"],"Again, when the wicked",["i","man"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"turneth"],"away from his wickedness that he hath committed, and doeth that which is lawful and right, he shall save his soul alive."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.28","order":"02.27.018.56161"},["b","28"],"Because he considereth, and turneth away from all his transgressions that he hath committed, he shall surely live, he shall not die."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.29","order":"02.27.018.56162"},["b","29"],"Yet saith the house of Israel, The way of the Lord is not",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_29a"},"equal"],". O house of Israel, are not my ways equal? are not your ways unequal?"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.30","order":"02.27.018.56163"},["b","30"],"Therefore I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_30a"},"judge"],"you, O house of Israel, every one according to his ways, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],". Repent, and turn",["i","yourselves"],"from all your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_30b"},"transgressions"],"; so iniquity shall not be your ruin."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.31","order":"02.27.018.56164"},["b","31"],"¶",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_31a"},"Cast"],"away from you all your transgressions, whereby ye have transgressed; and make you a new",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_31b"},"heart"],"and a",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_31c"},"new spirit"],": for why will ye",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_31d"},"die"],", O house of Israel?"],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.32","order":"02.27.018.56165"},["b","32"],"For I have no pleasure in the death of him that dieth, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],": wherefore turn",["i","yourselves,"],"and live ye."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.2a","order":"02.27.018.56166"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/31.29"},"Jer. 31:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/5.7"},"Lam. 5:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.4a","order":"02.27.018.56168"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justice"},"TG Justice"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sin"},"Sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.4b","order":"02.27.018.56170"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/punish"},"TG Punish"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.5a","order":"02.27.018.56172"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/heb/12.23"},"Heb. 12:23"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/76.69.66-69"},"D&C 76:69 (66–69)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.6a","order":"02.27.018.56174"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/123.1"},"Ps. 123:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.6b","order":"02.27.018.56176"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.37"},"2 Ne. 9:37"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.6c","order":"02.27.018.56178"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.24.22-26"},"D&C 42:24 (22–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.6d","order":"02.27.018.56180"},["b","6d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/18.19"},"Lev. 18:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.7a","order":"02.27.018.56182"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/22.26"},"Ex. 22:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/24.13"},"Deut. 24:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.15"},"Ezek. 33:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.7b","order":"02.27.018.56184"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/34.28.18-29"},"Alma 34:28 (18–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.8a","order":"02.27.018.56186"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/usury"},"TG Usury"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.11a","order":"02.27.018.56188"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/20.10"},"Lev. 20:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.12a","order":"02.27.018.56190"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.14.14-15"},"2 Ne. 13:14 (14–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/28.13.12-13"},"28:13 (12–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/4.12.11-13"},"Hel. 4:12 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.13a","order":"02.27.018.56192"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.4"},"Ezek. 33:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.14a","order":"02.27.018.56194"},["b","14a"],["span.small","HEB"],"like them."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.18a","order":"02.27.018.56196"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/cruelty"},"TG Cruelty"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.20a","order":"02.27.018.56198"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/sin"},"TG Sin"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.20b","order":"02.27.018.56200"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/accountability"},"TG Accountability"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/punish"},"Punish"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.20c","order":"02.27.018.56202"},["b","20c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.21a","order":"02.27.018.56204"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/repent"},"TG Repent"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.22a","order":"02.27.018.56206"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/forgive"},"TG Forgive"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/transgress"},"Transgress"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.23a","order":"02.27.018.56208"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.11"},"Ezek. 33:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/2.4.4,6"},"1 Tim. 2:4 (4, 6)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/3.9"},"2 Pet. 3:9"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pleasure"},"TG Pleasure"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.24a","order":"02.27.018.56210"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/3.20"},"Ezek. 3:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.24b","order":"02.27.018.56212"},["b","24b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.12.12-13,18"},"Ezek. 33:12 (12–13, 18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"24c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.24c","order":"02.27.018.56214"},["b","24c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/righteousness"},"TG Righteousness"],"."],["div",{"id":"24d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.24d","order":"02.27.018.56216"},["b","24d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.38"},"2 Ne. 9:38"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.25a","order":"02.27.018.56218"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.17"},"Ezek. 33:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.25b","order":"02.27.018.56220"},["b","25b"],["span.small","HEB"],"right or just."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.26a","order":"02.27.018.56222"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/apostasy-of-individuals"},"TG Apostasy of Individuals"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.26b","order":"02.27.018.56224"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/15.33.32-33"},"1 Ne. 15:33 (32–33)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/15.26"},"Mosiah 15:26"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/10.26"},"Moro. 10:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.27a","order":"02.27.018.56226"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.14"},"Ezek. 33:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"29a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.29a","order":"02.27.018.56228"},["b","29a"],["span.small","HEB"],"right or just."],["div",{"id":"30a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.30a","order":"02.27.018.56230"},["b","30a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.3.3,8"},"Ezek. 7:3 (3, 8)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.20"},"33:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"30b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.30b","order":"02.27.018.56232"},["b","30b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/transgress"},"TG Transgress"],"."],["div",{"id":"31a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.31a","order":"02.27.018.56234"},["b","31a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/20.7"},"Ezek. 20:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"31b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.31b","order":"02.27.018.56236"},["b","31b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/conversion"},"TG Conversion"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/heart"},"Heart"],"."],["div",{"id":"31c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.31c","order":"02.27.018.56238"},["b","31c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-new-spiritually-reborn"},"TG Man, New, Spiritually Reborn"],"."],["div",{"id":"31d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.31d","order":"02.27.018.56240"},["b","31d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/33.11"},"Ezek. 33:11"],"."]]}
